    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is totally flawless. It\u2019s been my absolute baby and I\u2019ve taken perfect care of it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
