    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements. The exterior paint retains its original deep-gloss luster, entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and uncreased, while the carpets and headliner are spotless. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive navigation, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, offering a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it was manufactured. It comes with a full, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians, ensuring total peace of mind. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
